title: Thom Hartmann Program - September 24 2013
description:
September 24, 2013
The Thom Hartmann Program 

Hour One: De-regulation...the real economic crisis of the day?  Bill Frezza, Competitive Enterprise Institute / Plus, have Republicans declared Ayn Rand Allahu Akbar on America?

Hour Two: There are no 'good guys with guns' - Noel Flasterstein, Gun Rights for You

Hour Three: Without privacy there can be no democracy...
